videos.headline: Brooks breaks free for 61-yard Vandy TD
videos.description: Vanderbilt freshman Keyon Brooks finds an opening and takes off in a foot race for a 61-yard touchdown vs. Northern Illinois.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brooks breaks free for 61-yard Vandy TD) 2019/9/28

videos.headline: Vandy's Hebert comes up with huge hit
videos.description: Northern Illinois' Jordan Nettles is leveled by Vanderbilt's Kenny Hebert but still manages to hold onto the ball.
